comments: Die Basslinie ist ausgezeichnet, insgesamt auch ein sehr schönes Lied, welches ich mir gerne öfter anhöre.
I saw Monolake while on acid in 2011.  It was amazing.

I am an old, old man, and I live in a tent in a wide and relentless forest far away from people. I rest my head on the trees and listen to them creak and chat, passing on the latest news. I try not to think about how I got here, painful memories of my life and loves, and what sense there can be in such a life. Instead, I enjoy the sounds and shapes that trees make, and how the breeze fills the air with life. This is my soundtrack.
